    "Id": "chassisdef_siorc_wolf_SIW-1",
    "Name": "Siorc Wolf",
    "Details": "The Siorc Wolf 1 features an impressive jump capacity of 120 meters, armed with twin ATM-6s and Class 20 Hyper Assault Gauss Rifles, complemented by a Watchdog CEWS for solid offensive capabilities. What truly sets this ‘Mech apart is its unique torso design. Instead of a traditional single pivot, it uses twin torso discs to allow torso twisting. This innovative mechanism protects the armor and CASE II mounts from damage while enabling faster rotation and a wider arc of fire. This design significantly enhances the pilot’s ability to engage enemies across a broader field without repositioning the entire mech.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.24</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
